    "description": "踏上史诗般的行动冒险之旅，成为Lumnis的下一位守护者，这是一个充满奇迹和神秘的秘密之地。<br>为了证明自己配得上这个角色，你必须探索黑暗的洞穴，与无情的敌人战斗，攀登许多高峰，最终实现你的命运。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900320/extras/a5c29bcb7c1ba7c7cb830da25b81aa89.avif?t=1717704499\" width=601 height=70 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900320/extras/15c2a7447c780fc1d8bee1a12e2dc8f9.webp?t=1717704499\" width=9 height=14 /></span> <strong>类似塞尔达的进程</strong><br>发现新的物品和工具，以便在旅程中取得进展。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900320/extras/da0b6cc214e5cefec3ab2a42c8372ada.poster.avif?t=1717704499\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900320/extras/da0b6cc214e5cefec3ab2a42c8372ada.webm?t=1717704499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900320/extras/da0b6cc214e5cefec3ab2a42c8372ada.mp4?t=1717704499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900320/extras/15c2a7447c780fc1d8bee1a12e2dc8f9.webp?t=1717704499\" width=9 height=14 /></span> <strong>灵魂般的扭曲战斗</strong><br>一种基于耐力的战斗系统，灵感来源于类似灵魂的类型，并经过扩展以适合游戏幻想。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900320/extras/a582b887843322364972238cbb8d9925.poster.avif?t=1717704499\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900320/extras/a582b887843322364972238cbb8d9925.webm?t=1717704499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900320/extras/a582b887843322364972238cbb8d9925.mp4?t=1717704499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900320/extras/15c2a7447c780fc1d8bee1a12e2dc8f9.webp?t=1717704499\" width=9 height=14 /></span> <strong>独特的攀登系统</strong><br>旨在为你提供运动自由和挑战的完美结合, 让你感觉像一个真正的攀岩者。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900320/extras/333188f9b894076e79ea267d6d3f4826.poster.avif?t=1717704499\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900320/extras/333188f9b894076e79ea267d6d3f4826.webm?t=1717704499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900320/extras/333188f9b894076e79ea267d6d3f4826.mp4?t=1717704499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900320/extras/15c2a7447c780fc1d8bee1a12e2dc8f9.webp?t=1717704499\" width=9 height=14 /></span> <strong>探索充满奇迹和神秘的土地</strong><br>从失落的废墟到茂密的森林和雪山，你会发现各种各样的环境和地方，每一个都有自己的特点。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900320/extras/a8fc82e3d49276619594568f9f3e819c.poster.avif?t=1717704499\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900320/extras/a8fc82e3d49276619594568f9f3e819c.webm?t=1717704499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900320/extras/a8fc82e3d49276619594568f9f3e819c.mp4?t=1717704499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900320/extras/15c2a7447c780fc1d8bee1a12e2dc8f9.webp?t=1717704499\" width=9 height=14 /></span> <strong>大气环境</strong><br>以大气视觉和声音为重点的简约风格化艺术风格。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900320/extras/78ec3776772cb78d67afd9789390ee1f.poster.avif?t=1717704499\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900320/extras/78ec3776772cb78d67afd9789390ee1f.webm?t=1717704499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900320/extras/78ec3776772cb78d67afd9789390ee1f.mp4?t=1717704499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
